title: 【ド★初見】太陽のしっぽ　その２
name: Inugami Korone

entries.text: My nose is totally stuffed up.
It's not just because I woke up or anything.
I don't have a fever or anything.
It's just my nose that is super blocked.
...don't find it hard to understand me, we're good.
Hold on, gonna drink some water.
It is definitely not hay fever.
"You're cute even with a stuffed nose."
You guys really are fine with anything.
What does "cute because your nose is stuffed" even mean?
Anything goes with you at this point.
You'd probably say something like that.
Eh? Is there pollen in the air?
Is this hay fever after all?
But if I admit it, the symptoms will get worse.
Thanks for coming to watch Koro-san. "Your existence is cute"? Thanks. Today...
It's part two of "Tail of the Sun," so...
Since I sound so nasal, I think I'll play a bit quietly today.
Yesterday... wait, the day before yesterday...
I checked the "KiKiKaiKai" archive, and it was so loud I closed it immediately.
I was like, "So noisy!" I don't know if I can clear this today...
But let's try. Can I stay quiet? If I scream with this stuffed nose...
That sounds like it'd be pretty bad, right?
I watched the whole thing earlier. A total hero.
A hero, a Dotechin. Okay, wait a sec. The sound might be loud, guys.
Watch your ears. I really hate that it's just my nose that's stuffed.
If it's gonna be like this, I wish everything was stuffed. "Sing a little"?
I think it's just this part.
I feel like it covers up Koune's nasal voice.
Wait, was I playing this with a controller?
I think it'll quiet down once the game starts.
We have 2 out of 23 segments of the tower built.
Does that mean I can replay 43 times? Like, retries.
The village has 2 million people now.
Once it starts, I'll check the volume...
How do I pick things up again?
So low game volume might be fine.
Is it made of this now?
Let's make today a chill stream.
♪ Gogon Gon with a stone axe ♪
Should I make Koune's face a bit bigger?
This guy's reaching the end of his lifespan.
He can live for quite a while.
I haven't really seen them die of old age yet.
This guy? Sleeping right away is cute.
Well, he's living his life to the fullest.
Fulfilling his duty as a human.
People in this era, at least.
I can hold this now, too.
The screen's a bit dark, huh.
So, there's a mammoth up there...
But we haven't gone down much.
We said we'd go down last time.
The pigs are kinda strong, though.
It's hard. Hit and run, hit and run... it's tough.
Are there mammoths down there? Would be nice if there were.
*Teko teko teko...* A Wagashi? Poor thing. This is a sweet, guys. Wow, amazing.
"Intelligence goes up." But what's the point of getting smarter?
What happens when you get smarter? Headbutts?
Does the population cap increase or something?
Wow, I ate all the flowers.
Oh, Culture Level goes up. Huh.
Thanks for being here in the middle of the day, expert.
Wow, them being bunched up like that makes them worth eating.
Ah, this. A button, A button.
Hey, I'm a monkey, but you're a monkey too!
Wait, wait, I'm gonna die, die, die!
Anything but drowning! Anything but drowning!
Oh no, it's almost time to sleep.
Is there really no map for this?
I hope land is close... I might die in the water.
Ah, a monkey. Should I finish it off?
The meat disappeared last time. The monkey meat might disappear too.
I blew my nose... Whoa, it disappeared!
Returning to nature way too fast. That's the law of nature, I guess.
It's beginner stuff. Some of you are working today, right? I was ego-searching...
"No wind-up animation?" Exactly. This guy lives too much by his desires.
It started snowing, so maybe there's a snowy mountain here too?
It's snowing. My voice is way too nasal, it's bad.
It's okay? My voice is totally different. When my nose is stuffed...
"Working a side job." "Went to an interview for a new job." Wow.
Pigs are tough... Thanks for watching while working. Don't get in trouble!
You shouldn't watch while working remotely!
I can't hold it. What is this?
People different from us live here?
It looks like a neighboring town.
Like the back side of a train station.
Let's raise the Culture Level with this.
So this is a body part object too.
Ah, there were flowers over there too.
But if it's a boob, there's only one.
Well, one boob is fine too, I guess.
Look, what do you guys think?
The flowers are crazy. But if flowers are blooming...
This is a boob. Eh? A boob?
I'll put it in. Just put it in.
That means the things I found so far...
Can I do it? Can I?
Let's go down again. It's scary but...
I ate a lot of heads.
I want to make the Brain pink.
Since I beat that one earlier, maybe it's listed.
Also, I want to try beating a fish.
Ah, was the right leg there?
I should beat new ones, I guess.
So I thought I might oversleep.
Don't go back yet, eat it.
I learned that from a video.
Because of that video, "Ostriches are idiots" is the only thing stuck in my head.
Ah, this guy runs away too.
I got one, so that's fine.
Threatening an ostrich with "Don't you care what happens to your family?" doesn't work.
Ostriches even forget their family's faces.
So threats don't work on ostriches.
I don't want to be an ostrich.
Every day is a first meeting with the zookeeper.
They think "Oh, a different person today" every time.
That's sad. Even though you see them every day.
"Koro-san, do you have a cold?" You can tell?
Maybe it's that voice thing? It feels like a cold, but everything else is fine.
I don't have a fever or anything, just a stuffy nose.
I don't think it's a cold though.
The skin on my nose is peeling.
But I found a new ingredient.
A Curl wouldn't be this shriveled.
Scary when things come from off-screen.
This is a Kujo Green Onion.
I want to go over there.
Whoa, sleeping here would be bad.
Sleeping on a slope is definitely bad.
Is it safe to sleep around here?
Even if I sleep here, please.
There's no face I can empathize with.
What to do... guess I'll pick this one.
Going down is dangerous after all.
Let's go hunt mammoths for a bit.
I'll hunt mammoths and explore a bit.
I want to finish the tower and explore.
"A beauty once in a thousand years."
This girl is definitely the Kanna Hashimoto of this era.
Like, her face is just different from everyone else's.
Sleep soon... but I can cross. I can cross.
Like "Shouldn't you stay quiet and rest?"
Enemies definitely come because of this snoring.
Korone talks in her sleep too, so I can't really judge.
I have absolutely no memory of it.
People who talk in their sleep...
I definitely can't pick a fight with a hippo.
"Hippos kill the most people in the savannah."
Can't pick a fight with Kaba (Hippo) and Kaba-chan.
What meat do you want to eat?
Do you want to try it?
Monkey is a bit... no thanks.
It's already lunchtime, but I'm sleepy.
What time did I get up? Today was late, 9... 9 o'clock?
Woke up cause I probably couldn't breathe.
Woke up cause my nose stopped up.
But I have a stream today.
Wondered if my nose would clear up by stream time.
It's not hard to talk or anything.
I'm fine, so I'm doing it.
Sorry for making you worry. Nose is stuffed... Ah, snowy mountain! I can see mammoths again!
Eh? Ah, carrying stone axe. Bam bam! Yay!
Stone axe carrying bam bam bam bam... Goro goro gon gon...
Okay, this should do it. Where are the Mammoth-chans?
I forget the location every time. Where was it? My sense of geography is non-existent.
But it was the snowy place. Where they usually are.
There were hippos too. Or things like hippos.
Let's do our best, both of us.
Let's both give it our all.
I wonder if you can see us fighting.
Alright, haven't we gotten much stronger?
Won't they invent cell phones soon?
First time seeing this. What is it?
Is this a body part too?
Like what Koune and everyone uses.
It looks just like a tetrapod.
Tetrapod, isn't the head too long?
If someone told me I could time slip to this primitive age, I absolutely wouldn't.
Not badmouthing the primitive age or anything.
But I don't really want to go.
Are there people who want to go?
Unless you're an engineer or something, wouldn't you not want to go?
Items are forbidden. No items allowed.
There are too many body parts.
It might be a miniature garden (Hakoniwa).
You'll die if you sleep there.
I'm scared I'll hit my head on it.
Probably the exit of this sandbox.
And the Cultural Level up is...
Am I running in the same spot?
Maybe I didn't need to return.
Right, this is a game about collecting tusks.
Oh crap, I forgot to jump while moving.
People seeing this for the first time today must be confused.
Let's go while picnicking around here.
When you hear someone's nasal voice...
Don't you want to blow your own nose?
Don't you want to clear your throat?
I feel like you'd want to do it too.
Right? You get it? Everyone's plans for today?
"Watching Koro-san all day." I know that, but aside from that.
Like going somewhere, or working tonight.
Ah, Koune's stream? Playing with Koro-san.
I'm happy you spend this time with me. You could watch movies instead.
Koune might not be able to go see it, but there's this movie "Together" playing. Anyone seen it?
If you don't know "Together," look it up. Looks interesting.
Going shopping? Ah right, nasal voice. I'll write "Nasal Voice".
Nasal voice... image of touching lips appeared.
Yeah yeah, that one. That's it.
Yep, nasal voice. I have a nasal voice today. Please bear with me.
"Lou Oshiba." A bit old isn't it?
Is the Mammoth location not fixed?
What would the two of us do?
Want to go see? I'll show you how it is now.
Still a long way to go.
Want to get to about the 10th step.
If we can see the ending today, I want to see it, but...
I have a nasal voice, so I won't push it.
Want to find a mammoth spot.
Do I have to go back every time?
Eh, Koune recently made a debut.
Where you can rent phone chargers.
Recently... ah, lifespan is getting bad.
Eh, if you don't return it, don't you get charged forever?
I used to carry a charger like that.
But recently I rent from Charge Spot.
If I can't see it, I get anxious.
The security of knowing batteries are in there.
I don't get much empathy for this.
By the progress of this world.
I can't use electronic money either.
I don't use cards much either.
It's scary. Invisible money accumulating is scary. I'm afraid of invisible things.
I want to see. I want to see everything. It's kinda scary.
"Cash faction." Good, there are people like that. Angry monster.
"Be careful with words like digitization and unified management."
Be careful of things that advertise that?
You mean I shouldn't say "digitization" too much?
Hard to tell what's a scam.
No no no, Olive is different.
No way. Don't want to make it.
Even though I did whatever I wanted.
Everyone was a bit on edge though.
I didn't say anything like that, so it was fine.
Bring a cute one, a cute one.
I don't really get it but...
Ah, a fairly normal person came.
These rough polygons add to the creepiness.
What is this face in the dark?
Maybe I shouldn't have pressed the button.
Right, it's creepy. A bit creepy.
How is it? 4 steps... ah, became 5!
Looks like it's made of wood.
Or rather, 2 more levels to cap. Do your best.
You forget to save in Steam games sometimes, right? No auto-save?
I'd hate a bow and arrow.
I'm bad with bows in Monster Hunter too.
Koune looks like she'd have bad aim.
Let's go pun. Let's go pun.
Let's go pun. Swinging a rock and throwing it.
Need spares. This probably won't get empathy, but...
Like in One Piece fight scenes.
Takes it out of his pocket.
"If this drags on, won't you run out?"
You get it? I think about silly things like that.
I'm the type to worry about that.
It's anime and manga, so it's impossible.
Running out might be a plot point, but...
But I'm like "Okay? Okay? Can't watch!"
"He might be out of ammo, what to do."
Wait, this guy has no lifespan left.
Looks like the edge of the world.
Don't want to die in the water.
If I don't go up, everyone dies.
Lifespan is close, want to swim?
It's dark and hard to see.
This guy is done for anyway.
Lifespan will run out before jumping.
Ugh, impossible. This is the worst.
This guy has a long life.
I want to hunt as many mammoths as I can.
This eerie feeling, I kinda like the rough polygons.
I like the rough polygons of this era.
Rough polygons underwater are super scary.
The sea in this game is clear, so not too scary.
If it was darker and deeper, it'd be terrifying.
It might be a god game.
What happens when we clear it?
If we climb to the sun...
I want you guys to play it too.
Koune has died a lot though.
Apparently the population or remaining cavemen changes the ending.
I don't know, but that seems to be a condition.
What? You don't want to play?
Playing confusing games on stream is good.
And even for games like this, there are experts.
There's usually someone who answers if you ask.
So I'm doing it quieter than usual.
But does the nasal voice bother you?
"Shouldn't you cure it first?" Do you think that?
"Want you to spoil me with nasal voice."
"Want nasal voice ASMR." What the heck.
Hey, pass it over, the three of you.
"Is there demand for nasal voice?" Heh.
Ah crap, doing the same thing again.
Koune definitely wants coffee or tea in the morning.
Want to wake up with that.
Calorie Mate is for long streams.
If there's milk, it's totally fine.
Said there weren't any, then found one.
Don't soak in the tub. Isn't it annoying?
I wash. I wash, but I don't get in even if I fill it.
Really a pain. Shouldn't be lazy.
It's about priorities. What you spend time on.
While in the bath, isn't it boring?
Koune doesn't have a TV in the bath.
Don't want to use phone in bath.
Don't want to read either. Half-body bath and reading is fine for some.
Personally, Koune hates doing things in the bath.
If you don't mind doing things in the bath, fine. But for Koune, it's painful.
"Sweating is good." I'd rather get out warm...
...put on fluffy pajamas and lie on the sofa.
Being in water for a long time... I'm bad with it.
Want to go on land. "Let me on land quickly!"
"I can swim 300m." Maybe 50m if I try.
"Do you like saunas?" Sauna is boring... Stop it. Stop now?
Don't know what to do in saunas either.
Cute, keep this one. Rare. What happened here? What is this?
Controller... this is bad. Everyone... no...
This is bad. From afar it's okay.
Only crazy ones. Okay, Mammoth time.
If I know the reason, I'll understand.
Why did they become like that?
Tell me the meaning. Tell me how it happened.
Are they wearing makeup? On their face?
"One looks like me, is it okay?"
"You're under arrest" type faces are common.
Can you hear the button mashing too?
If I beat two and return, do I get two?
Want to try? Easy to beat anyway.
"Thought voice was cute, turned out to be nasal."
Means I sound cuter than usual?
Everyone says nasal voice is cute.
Playing "Tail of the Sun" in the afternoon.
If Koune's voice plays at work...
Will they be like "What's that cute voice?"
Don't know the ending at all.
Not ending, if Culture Level goes up 1 more...
Feel like I'm getting called cute more than usual.
"Not popular" (motenai)? Not that kind of "motenai" (can't hold).
I take taxis a lot recently.
But I want to listen to music in the taxi.
But even if I wear earphones, the driver talks to me a lot.
I try to signal "I'm wearing earphones"...
It's not that I don't want to talk...
I want to be left alone a bit.
They might be trying to be nice.
Want to hunt mammoth when I wake up.
Well, I listen to Koyori too.
Don't know conditions for memorial dive.
When I bring back enough mammoths?
When I bring back lots of meat?
With this much food, it's fine.
It's a Fes at this point.
Normal stream maybe? Is that okay?
Looks like I can catch fish too.
Spear is the end of this era.
Does attack power go up by eating dropped items?
If I raise strength, it should go up.
What is Saruganseki? I don't know.
If you don't know, you don't.
I end up just calling their name.
Anyone like that moment? Among listeners.
Recently putting sasami in hotpot too.
But thigh with skin is good too.
Don't sleep the moment I think about it.
Talking about food makes me hungry.
Sasami has a pipe thing attached.
Hate that. Is that the tendon?
Ate Cream Genmai Bran before stream.
Surprised. Thought it was water, it was tea.
Ah, crap, tree is normal tree.
Koune likes eating with ponzu best.
Like a folded 1000 yen bill face.
Remote island seems to be there.
No shoulder? Was there no shoulder?
If tower reaches 23 steps, reach sun and clear.
*Munch munch* Nasal voice tough? Not tough.
Sounds tough to you. 9 endings crazy? 9?
9 endings apparently. What does that mean? Curious.
Curious but looking for mammoths. Not mammoth, hippo.
Mysteriously many lol. Changes a little? Or a lot?
I wonder. Doing this on holiday is crazy.
Crazy on holiday afternoon. Fun though.
Took time to get used to.
Necklace made of source scale tusks.
Hunting mammoth, collecting tusks, building tower.
Hunting mammoth, collecting tusks, building tower.
Collecting mammoth... no, hunting mammoth, collecting tusks, building tower.
Couldn't bring ending making time? Curious.
Reach is longer. Easy to fight.
Bad, don't come. Can counter though.
Long time no see "Nasal voice" question.
Was night time always this long?
The battery in the virtual space has run out.
Just wait, I'll be right back.
Koone fell asleep too, right at sleeping time.
Ah, I can come back right away.
It asked for a login show.
Wait a second, what the heck.
Don't ask me to login every single time.
I think I made it back with this.
There's no GPS in this era, so...
But you know, I'm curious about this.
If you left one invention from the modern era...
Just one item here before going back...
Really just, how do I put it...
It's impossible, can't be done, absolutely.
Even if you wanted to, you can't do it.
Would it go in a weird direction?
Even if I think about that stuff...
I like thinking about meaningless things.
Primitve man sleeps too much? Hey.
Aren't they going to sleep earlier?
You guys sleep a decent amount, right?
When I streamed until 1 or 2 AM...
And ask "What time do you wake up?"
A lot of people say "I wake up at 6."
You guys aren't sleeping at all.
It's rich coming from Koone, but...
"You play until clear even when it doesn't say Endurance Stream."
When I don't write "Endurance," it's when I'm not confident.
If I write "Endurance" and can't endure, I feel kinda iffy about it myself.
You guys tell me "It's totally fine," but...
I feel iffy about it personally.
So I don't want to use the word "Endurance" when I lack confidence.
That's why even during Mario Galaxy...
I didn't know how long it would be.
I'm going to finish without hunting a Mammoth!
Well, I guess that was good.
I've been playing for quite a while...
But I don't think I understand anything.
I want to think about various things after seeing the ending.
Night time is early... feels like it's getting faster.
"Is it a game worth theorizing over?"
Maybe I shouldn't talk about it after seeing only one...
Recently, there are no Mammoths at all.
Did things like "colds" exist since ancient times?
Had a fever close to 40 degrees...
And always goes to the hospital thinking "This is bad!" but...
"Ah, it's just a fever from a cold."
It just ends, not the flu.
And you tell me it's nothing?
Like when you bump into something...
It hurts so much but you're uninjured.
"Why is there no external wound when it hurts this much?!"
Oi, just leave a scratch at least!
It makes me anxious if there's no wound.
I hate it... bruises make me more anxious than cuts.
Like... a visible wound makes me feel safer somehow.
What is it... when it's bleeding and swelling inside the skin, it gets really scary.
Can you not resolve it on the inside?
Like I'm left out of the loop.
Can you include me in the group?
Can you let me join the group?
Recently, Mio-sha is the only one I've met.
It's not a story about Mio-sha.
I took off my socks for Mio-sha...
And said "Look, this is where it's broken."
Ah, but photo of the wound... umm, morning...
I sent it to my manager... did I?
Maybe I worry too much, but I didn't want them to think I was lying.
"Fracture? No way," I know they aren't people who think like that, but...
I thought it's better to have proof.
You send hospital diagnosis papers to the company, right?
There's that too, so I thought I'd send a pic just in case.
I edited it a bit, properly.
Edited it so even people who are bad with gore can see it.
Like, "It looks a bit like this."
There he is, there he is.
Usually you should send the diagnosis...
Send the diagnosis paper, I guess.
I said "Excuse me, sending an image for now."
The village population isn't increasing much...
Is it because I'm not eating enough grain?
Or because I'm not bringing back enough meat?
But like, how do I say it... other people's wounds...
Other people's wounds, or blood, some people absolutely can't look at it.
Being sent a picture of a bent leg.
But you know, Koone's new manager loves splatter.
So I can totally send photos of fractures.
"Eh~ I'm happy! Let's talk about it sometime," I said.
People don't usually say "I love splatter"...
Not many people tell you that.
And for a manager to like splatter...
I haven't asked what splatter movies she likes yet.
I'll ask her lots of things from now on.
But she said she got hooked on SAW, I think.
She watched the SAW series and got hooked on splatter or something...
The moment I entered the water, lifespan appeared. Does water affect it?
That's not it right? Stop it-nu.
SAW is interesting after all. Yeah, it is.
Oh! Ah, hippo. Should I eat it? Dangerous.
I'll get hungry. Gonna be starving. Well, fine. Whatever.
People watching while playing Mahjong or something?
Feel like I'm getting told I'm cute more than usual.
But only occasionally because it's nasal congestion...
As expected, most people are doing something while watching.
Making Gunpla. Eh, Doria? Fast. Is Dragon Quest easy this time?
DS was the easiest. Or rather...
Is it even easier than that?
No, it's good that it's easier to play.
Habit makes me want to go back.
In the snowy mountains, when I defeat an animal, habit makes me want to go back.
"Is Koro-san the type who doesn't want to play remakes?"
It's not that I don't want to play them.
Anyway, right now it's Tail of the Sun.
For now, rather than Kiefer's tail...
Koone wants to chase the Tail of the Sun.
Aiya don don don. Thank you.
Yes, let's go. Ran ran ran.
Go ahead, go ahead, please use it.
This is how it looks now.
I don't really know if this changed or not.
I'll show you just in case.
Population isn't growing much anymore though.
Is there a max population limit?
Oh, it's getting close. Getting close.
You guys better be ready for the ending.
Let's get it to Level 20 for now.
Wouldn't it be easier if I get it to Level 20?
Call me if it's about to happen.
You have no intention of watching right now!
If the remaining number of primitive men changes the ending...
Well, seems like we can see about 2 endings?
I could reduce numbers by killing them.
By the next time I sleep, I want to find and defeat a Mammoth.
What if I purposely make it the last person and collect the final tusk?
"Ending changes with symbols on the body too."
So with these tattoos I can see 5 or 6 endings?
If you didn't tell me, Koone probably wouldn't do it.
You guys mind them too, right?
But when it comes to this game...
I read the included manual, though.
"Recent V-tuber community is loud about spoilers."
I understand the urge to say it.
Maybe it's not good for Koone to say "I understand the urge to spoil" here.
But I understand, the urge to say it.
Especially if you like the game.
"I want them to see that god-tier event..."
Yeah, yeah. It also reduces the enjoyment.
Well, if it's a first playthrough, you won't notice things, can't be helped.
Just a bit, well, the frustration, right?
But if you play just reading spoilers, then...
It stops being that person's playthrough.
Of course, playing without spoilers until clearing is probably better.
Probably better, but this problem is difficult.
Because the people who say things will never disappear.
It becomes about how much we can ignore it.
After all, people other than regular viewers will absolutely come.
People coming just for that game.
No matter how much I write in the description, say it verbally, or pin comments, there are people who say it.
At that point, we just have to deal with it on our end.
My lifespan is running out like this.
People who don't read won't read.
If I ask, they probably can.
If I say "I don't like these comments, please delete them," they'll do it.
I've never asked though, Koone hasn't.
Bots delete them without asking though.
This became a super serious talk while playing Tail of the Sun.
Maybe this game is actually deep.
Spoil the Mammoth location for me!
Like in Minecraft, fence them in...
Give them grass, make them breed.
Make them breed, then hit them from one block higher.
But you know, it's something everyone told me...
Don't know if it was a long time ago, but...
"If there are 100 people, a stream that satisfies all 100 is impossible."
We had a talk like that a long time ago.
Koone wants to be liked by everyone.
If there are 100 people, I want all 100 to have fun.
Since I started streaming with that mindset...
I feel much more at ease.
Some people hate streamers who scream.
Some people want to watch quietly.
Some people like the nasal voice, some hate it.
Where can I meet a Mammoth?
Well, can't be helped. That's life too.
Isn't it faster if I die?
This is the end for me.
The God of Death should be coming for me soon.
Won't work if I don't eat...
Let's go for a woman. Woman.
This is sexy. The back is...
Right? Glad I wasn't born in the primitive era.
I couldn't stand this. But maybe I was born then, in reincarnation.
We might have experienced it. Just don't have the memories.
You guys might have experienced it too.
I like thinking about that stuff too.
Maybe I was on the Mammoth side.
Uwah, got woken up means she'll sleep again.
Danger of second sleep is high.
I'm a woman who gives up fast.
Is this the max rank for the house?
Is house rank maxed out with this?
Oh my, oh my, I wonder.
Eh~ I want to be called cute.
But if you tell me nasal voice is...
It was precious Calorie Mate time.
Oh, taking paid leave and watching with a drink?
What sound does a Mammoth make?
Must be in this snowy mountain.
It counts as one per kill, probably.
There's a guy with an elephant face.
Once I hit Level 20, I should separate the saves.
If I'm seeing multiple endings, dragging it out is...
Sorry, I'm bad with numbers earlier.
"Curious about the dotted islands on the right."
Wanna go see? Just a bit.
I don't. You guys play? Everyone plays?
But I don't know where to go to reach the dotted islands.
I like the picture quality, but...
